title: Eight Groups of Papyrus Fragments Inscribed in Demotic and Greek
description: A large group of fragments in various scripts.  Prior to 1966, the fragments were divided into subsets a-e.  See the following subdivisions.
credit_line: Bequest of Theodora Wilbour from the collection of her father, Charles Edwin Wilbour
